name: Disruption - Original
description:
After about 18 months of real art exploration this piece was a departure in 
 style for me and represents a disturbance below the surface that wanted to express itself to the world. How often do we have something within us that is below the surface wanting to come out but we suppress it out of fear? This energy was a birth for me into finding my own creative voice, trusting and flowing with it.This is part of a series exploring the disturbance. This image is the full artwork and whoever buys this is entitled to the real world artwork, shipped anywhere in the world. I will also be releasing 1 of "prints" of close up details of this work and the other parts of the series. This is my first NFT.
